@startuml diagram-bruin-run1
scale 1.5
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #e3f2fd
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #1565c0

title Run 1: Initial Load  (Jan-Jun 2022)

start
:1 parquet file in data/\n**1080 reviews** (Jan-Jun 2022);

:**raw_reviews**\nReads all parquet files\nCreates a table with every review;
note right
  Bruin runs **3 quality checks**
  before anything downstream can start:

  Is every rating non-null?
  Is every rating in [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]?
  Is every review_date non-null?
end note

:**monthly_summary**\nGROUP BY month, filter to Jan-Jun\n(the date range we passed on the CLI)\nStrategy: **delete+insert**;
note right
  **3 more checks** on the output:

  Is every review_month non-null?
  Is every review_month unique?
  Is every n_reviews positive?
end note

:Result: **6 rows** in monthly_summary\n| Jan | Feb | Mar | Apr | May | Jun |;
stop

@enduml
